title: Nightwing-80`s
description:
Movie Description
An Indian tribal deputy faces a dark, menacing terror as he sets out to destroy a huge flock of vampire bats. In order to do so, he must enter the very cave in which they live.

Credits 
Cast: Nick Mancuso 
Director: Arthur Hiller 

Synopsis
When gruesome, disease-ridden vampire bats invade an Indian reservation in New Mexico, a cop, a nurse and a bat expert band together in a desperate effort to save the town.
